::Zardus::

Zardus slashes away the last of the vines, looking at the empty corridor beyond. He puts away the sword and proceeds slowly again, motioning for Wheeljack and Hurricane to follow him. His scanners determine that they were approaching whatever was functional, but they couldn't tell him more.
